{
  "text": "Murders provide a consistent measure through which we can investigate what changes were occurring when crack cocaine markets were introduced. 16 While we focus on murder, there is evidence that related outcomes like assaults and gunshot wounds during this period moved in line with murder rates [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
